# Theme tokens

All colors and fonts live under `:root` in `theme.css`. Reference them
with `var(--…)`, never hardcode hex.

## Palette

| Token              | Value     | Use                                 |
| ------------------ | --------- | ----------------------------------- |
| `--ink`            | `#14120B` | Dark background + main text         |
| `--ink-soft`       | `#26251E` | Slightly lighter ink                |
| `--body`           | `#3A382E` | Body text                           |
| `--muted`          | `#6B6960` | Secondary text                      |
| `--subtle`         | `#9E9C90` | Tertiary text (footer, captions)    |
| `--line`           | `#E6E5DD` | Borders, dividers                   |
| `--paper`          | `#F7F7F4` | Light background ("latte cream")    |
| `--white`          | `#FFFFFF` | Pure white (cards, code highlights) |
| `--accent`         | `#5C5A52` | Warm grey accent (top stripes, rules)|
| `--accent-soft`    | `#E6E5DD` | Soft accent for callout backgrounds |

## Typography

| Token         | Value                                   |
| ------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| `--font-sans` | `Inter` (UI, headlines, body)           |
| `--font-mono` | `JetBrains Mono` (code, numbers, eyebrows) |

## Rules

- ❌ Don't add hex colors outside `:root`. New colors → new tokens.
- ❌ Don't change a token's name once it's used in HTML — search/replace
  across both `template/index.html` and
  `examples/cursor-nexo-security/index.html` if you must rename.
- ✅ To retint the deck, change `--ink` / `--paper` / `--accent` /
  `--line`. Every component will follow.
- ✅ When the user asks for a "different palette" or "brand colors",
  edit `:root` only. Don't touch component CSS.

## Component overrides

Component classes (`.card`, `.stat`, `.code`, `.cmp`, `.callout`, …)
already reference tokens. Don't override them at the slide level —
extend the component class instead.
